com.azure.android.storage.blob.models

Annotation Type TransferInfo.State


  • @Retention(value=SOURCE)
public static @interface TransferInfo.State
    The current lifecycle state of the transfer.

    • Field Detail

      • STARTED

        public static final int STARTED
        Used to indicate that the transfer request is accepted by system.

      • RECEIVED_PROGRESS

        public static final int RECEIVED_PROGRESS
        Used to indicate that a part of transfer is completed and the current progress can be retrieved from TransferInfo.getProgress().

      • SYSTEM_PAUSED

        public static final int SYSTEM_PAUSED
        Used to indicate that the transfer is paused by the system because transfer constraints are not met or resources are not available. System will resume the transfer once constraints, resource requirements are satisfied.

      • USER_PAUSED

        public static final int USER_PAUSED
        Used to indicate that the transfer is paused by the user. The user has to request resume for a transfer in this state to continue.

      • RESUMED

        public static final int RESUMED
        Used to indicate that the transfer that was paused is resumed.

      • COMPLETED

        public static final int COMPLETED
        Used to indicate that the transfer has been completed.

      • FAILED

        public static final int FAILED
        Used to indicate that the transfer has been failed.

      • CANCELLED

        public static final int CANCELLED
        Used to indicate that the transfer is cancelled.
